chrome.browsingData

Top-Level Variables
browsingData: ChromeBrowsingData
Classes
ChromeBrowsingData

Use the chrome.browsingData API to remove browsing data from a user's local profile.

Top-Level Variables

static final ChromeBrowsingData browsingData

Accessor for the chrome.browsingData namespace.

Class ChromeBrowsingData

Methods

Future<dynamic> remove(dynamic options, dynamic dataToRemove)

Clears various types of browsing data stored in a user's profile.

dataToRemove The set of data types to remove.

callback Called when deletion has completed.

Future<dynamic> removeAppcache(dynamic options)

Clears websites' appcache data.

callback Called when websites' appcache data has been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeCache(dynamic options)

Clears the browser's cache.

callback Called when the browser's cache has been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeCookies(dynamic options)

Clears the browser's cookies and server-bound certificates modified within a particular timeframe.

callback Called when the browser's cookies and server-bound certificates have been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeDownloads(dynamic options)

Clears the browser's list of downloaded files (_not_ the downloaded files themselves).

callback Called when the browser's list of downloaded files has been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeFileSystems(dynamic options)

Clears websites' file system data.

callback Called when websites' file systems have been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeFormData(dynamic options)

Clears the browser's stored form data (autofill).

callback Called when the browser's form data has been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeHistory(dynamic options)

Clears the browser's history.

callback Called when the browser's history has cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeIndexedDB(dynamic options)

Clears websites' IndexedDB data.

callback Called when websites' IndexedDB data has been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeLocalStorage(dynamic options)

Clears websites' local storage data.

callback Called when websites' local storage has been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removePasswords(dynamic options)

Clears the browser's stored passwords.

callback Called when the browser's passwords have been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removePluginData(dynamic options)

Clears plugins' data.

callback Called when plugins' data has been cleared.

Future<dynamic> removeWebSQL(dynamic options)

Clears websites' WebSQL data.

callback Called when websites' WebSQL databases have been cleared.

Future<dynamic> settings()

Reports which types of data are currently selected in the 'Clear browsing data' settings UI. Note: some of the data types included in this API are not available in the settings UI, and some UI settings control more than one data type listed here.
